title: Saara
description: Saara ia an On-demand beauty service app with e-commerce. Tools and frameworks used in this project are Flutter, MobX, Firebase Messaging for push notifications. Integrated some payment gataeways like khalti and esewa.

title: College Nepal Members
description: Admin app for college admins who are the members of College Nepal web portal. Tools and frameworks I used in this project are Flutter, MVVM.

title: Books Timothy
description: Books Timothy is a mobile app launched in 2023 to access books written by Dr. Timothy Aryal. Developed with Flutter and Firebase, it offers a user-friendly interface and real-time data sync. Available on the Google Play Store, the app is actively maintained for optimal performance.

title: Smart Nagar
description: Smart Nagar is a mobile app developed in 2023 to bridge the gap between local government and the public. Created this app while I was working at Everestwalk Groups Pvt. Ltd. This app was made with Flutter. Abailable on the Google Play Store as Dakshinkali Municipality.

title: PJC Song Book
description: PJC Song Book is a mobile app which was developed in 2022 to enable users to access the lyrics and chords of songs. Using Flutter and Provider State Management, this app offers a smooth and intuitive experience for musicians and music enthusiasts.
